:"<h2>Hi Jigoshoppers!</h2>\n<p>Our development team has been busy at work with the release of Jigoshop eCommerce and &#8211; as you might have noticed by our last <a href="https://www.jigoshop.com/devblog-jigoshop-ecommerce-2-0-10/">/dev/blog post</a> &#8211; it wasn&#8217;t really a piece of cake 😉 . Long story short &#8211; here&#8217;s a list of the recently released stable extensions, adapted to be compatible with Jigoshop eCommerce &#8211; the ones most frequently requested by our users. The next round is coming soon, so you might want to consider visiting our Facebook Page, as well as keeping track of our blog entries here, at jigoshop.com :).<br />\nOh, and by the way &#8211; If you notice any potential bugs <a href="https://www.jigoshop.com/contact/">contact us</a> &#8211; your feedback is very important to us :).<span id="more-51675"></span></p>\n<h2>Recently Updated Extensions</h2>\n<ul style="list-style-type: none;">\n<li><a href="https://www.jigoshop.com/product/t-com-pay-way-pro-payment-gateway/"><img style="height: 30%; width: 30%; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;" src="https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/tcom.png" />T-Com Payway Gateway</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://www.jigoshop.com/product/jigoshop-tpay-com-payment-gateway/"><img style="height: 30%; width: 30%; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;" src="https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/tpay.png" alt="" />Tpay Gateway</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://www.jigoshop.com/product/paymill-payment-gateway-for-jigoshop/"><img style="height: 30%; width: 30%; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;" src="https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/paymill1.png" alt="" />Paymill Payment Gateway</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://www.jigoshop.com/product/fedex-shipping-rates/"><img style="height: 30%; width: 30%; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;" src="https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/fedex.png" alt="" />Fedex Shipping Method</a></li>\n