. In such case, it is probably wise to mention that Jigoshop requires WordPress. What is WordPress? WordPress is an extremely robust CMS (content management system) <a class="read-more" href="https://www.jigoshop.com/blog/post/wordpress-advantage/">Read More</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.jigoshop.com/blog/post/wordpress-advantage/">WordPress Advantage</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.jigoshop.com">Jigoshop</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Michael Stone";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2815:"<p>If you are reading this, then you are most likely considering the usage of Jigoshop. In such case, it is probably wise to mention that Jigoshop requires WordPress.</p>\n<h2>What is WordPress?</h2>\n<p>WordPress is an extremely robust CMS (content management system) available and has many advantages.<span id="more-50379"></span></p>\n<h2>Ease of Use</h2>\n<p>The greatest advantage of WordPress is that is easy to manage. You can quickly add pages, blog posts, products, and images without needing to write any code.</p>\n<p>This ability allows for content creators and business people to focus on the content they are creating or business they are running as opposed to waiting for someone else to place the content for them. As a result, the content creation time is drastically reduced.</p>\n<h2>Inexpensive to Implement</h2>\n<p>Depending on the complexity, WordPress sites are Inexpensive to build. To start, WordPress already has all of the essential elements needed for a website. Because of this, you are already saving money that you would alternatively spend on building up the base of your site. There is no sense in reinventing the wheel.</p>\n<p>There is also an abundance of WordPress themes available. Themes reduce time because they are prebuilt website frontends that contain the site layout and appearance features.</p>\n<h2>High Availability of Themes and Plugins</h2>\n<p>With the popularity of WordPress, it is not hard to fathom that there are tons of developers working on WordPress components. There is a huge supply of WordPress themes and plugins available for use. Moreover, if you cannot find what you want, then there is most likely a developer not too far away.</p>\n<h2>Search Engines</h2>\n<p>WordPress’ code allows search engines to index your site efficiently because the code is so clean and organized. Every item on the site has it is meta-identifier, and that helps even more.</p>\n<h2>Jigoshop eCommerce</h2>\n<p>What we like the most about WordPress is how seamlessly we have been able to develop the Jigoshop eCommerce plugin. The combination of WordPress and Jigoshop eCommerce make it simple to sell products. This ease allows for your business to focus on selling your product or service rather than worry about the website.</p>\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n<p>So as you have read, WordPress has many advantages. Main advantages are that it is simple and cost effective to implement; there is an abundance of themes and plugins readily available, and most importantly to us is that it allows us to develop Jigoshop eCommerce, which we regard as the best eCommerce plugin available!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.jigoshop.com/blog/post/wordpress-advantage/">WordPress Advantage</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.jigoshop.com">Jigoshop</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:60:"https://www.jigoshop.com/blog/post/wordpress-advantage/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"